description:
Noona is a marketplace for services and experiences. 

In Iceland (our home country), "Noona" means "now". 

Our goal is to help you book all of your appointments in a single app, without having to make a single phone call, whenever and wherever. So why not now? 

Whether you need a hair cut or a beauty session, a psychologist or a chiropractor, a dentist or a massage - or if your dog just really needs grooming - we've got you covered. 

- Discover the best service providers near you.
- Add your favorites to your home screen for easy access later on.
- See all of your upcoming appointments in one place.
- Move or cancel appointments without making a phone call.

It's a win-win for you and the ones you are booking with. You save time and don't need to make any phone calls, and they don't have to pick up the phone while they are busy with a client (how annoying is that, right?)

Join the revolution today and start booking all your appointments on Noona. 

It's free, and always will be.

Welcome to the world of simplified crafting: YarnPal is the app that brings your knitting and crochet skills to life in no time. Simply snap a photo, follow step-by-step instructions, and create personalised projects—anytime, anywhere.

YarnPal is your daily companion for knitting and crochet, giving you easy access to tutorials, patterns, and design inspiration. Try it now with our free trial and unlock a world of stitches, motifs, and creative possibilities—perfect for both beginners and experienced makers!

What Can YarnPal Do?
1. Snap a Photo, Learn a Stitch
Seen a stitch you love? Take a photo, and YarnPal will tell you its name and show you how to do it. Picking up new stitches is quick and easy!
2. Step-by-Step Pattern Help
Stuck on a pattern? Upload it to YarnPal. The app will break it down for you and help you keep track of your place as you work through each row. You can even adjust the pace to suit your needs.
3. Creative AI Tools
Get Pattern Ideas: Lacking inspiration? Let YarnPal’s AI suggest new patterns for scarves, shawls, and other creative projects.
Fix Mistakes: Made an error? YarnPal can spot and help you fix it.
Understand Charts and Symbols: Struggling with pattern charts? YarnPal explains the symbols so you can follow along with confidence.
4. Ask the AI Coach
Have a question about knitting or crochet? Ask the AI Coach anything! From basic stitches to advanced techniques, get instant answers and helpful advice.
5. Personalise Your Projects
Want to make something unique? Adjust sizes, styles, and patterns to match your ideas. YarnPal helps you create truly one-of-a-kind pieces.

Who Is YarnPal For?
1. Beginners
New to knitting or crochet? YarnPal makes learning simple, with clear steps and helpful tips to get you started with confidence.
2. Hobbyists
Already enjoy knitting or crochet? Use YarnPal to try out new tools, tackle tricky patterns, and customise your projects. Take your craft to the next level!
3. Experts
Even for advanced crafters, YarnPal saves you time and sparks fresh ideas. Design better patterns, fix issues efficiently, and stay motivated.

Why Use YarnPal?
With YarnPal, crafting is:
Easy: Learn stitches and patterns stress-free.
Fun: Get creative and try something new.
Organised: Easily keep track of projects and progress.

Join the YarnPal Community
Connect with knitters and crocheters from around the world to share ideas, showcase your work, and get inspired. With YarnPal, you’ll never craft alone.

Start Your YarnPal Journey Today!
Download YarnPal now and see what you can create. Whether it’s your first simple scarf or an intricate piece of your own design, YarnPal will guide you every step of the way. Let’s make something amazing together!

Night Sky is a powerful AI personal planetarium.

Quickly identify stars, planets, constellations and satellites above by simply holding your iPhone, iPad or Apple Watch to the Night Sky!  This is all done magically.  Whether you’re looking for a constellation, or the International Space Station, let Night Sky direct you to it, then explore the object in AR!

FEATURE SET: 

- NIGHT SKY + AURA (Night Sky + Aura Subscription required) - Your Personal AI Super Astronomer!  Ask Night Sky Aura virtually anything about Space and it will know the answer.  Night Sky Aura fully interfaces with features within Night Sky, to direct you to objects you’re interested in, provide information on anything to do with astronomy, or even show you how the sky looks on the other side of the world!  With your own personal AI Super Astronomer right by your side, Night Sky Aura becomes the new natural way to interact with the sky above! 

- SKY TAGS - Make Night Sky yours, by adding personal Sky Tags to the map!  Pin Sky Tags to objects in the sky to save for future reference, and share them via iMessage so others can find them!  Sky Tags can be categorized, and are completely personal to you.  Maybe you want to tag a star as a memorial to someone, or tag something you’d like to observe later that night.  You can even add Astrophotography photos and observation notes to your Sky Tags!  

- CONNECTED STARGAZING (+ Feature) - Connected Stargazing is a revolutionary new feature that utilizes SharePlay in iOS 15.1, allowing you to stargaze with others when you are apart!  Start a FaceTime Audio call with those who you would like to stargaze with, then create a session by adding objects for everyone to find in the sky!

- SPATIAL AUDIO OBJECT NAVIGATION - Using AirPods Pro or AirPods Max, search for an object when automatic sky tracking is on, and Night Sky will make the star, planet or constellation ‘chirp’ in the 360° soundscape, assisting you to navigate to the object with sound!

- AR SKY WINDOW - Erase the ceiling of your bedroom, lounge or classroom with AR!  Night Sky intelligently detects the ceiling or other flat surface in a room, and can make it magically disappear to reveal the sky behind it!  

- BILLIONS OF STARS!  (+ Feature) - Space is vast, so Night Sky has been hyper charged with over 1.7 BILLION STARS streamed from the cloud!  With a new super deep zoom (greater than 10X before), prepare to delve deeper into space than you ever imagined!

- MAPS UI - A clean and familiar interface with Search features including Quick Find, intelligent Night Red Mode, Light Pollution indicator and easy to use menu, prepare to navigate Night Sky quicker than ever before!

- AR PLANETARY PORTALS & AR GRAND ORRERY (+ Features) - Step onto the surface of other planets by placing AR portals around your room!  Or walk around the entire Solar System using the newly refreshed interactive Grand Orrery!

- NIGHT SKY WATCH AR - Night Sky magically comes to life on Apple Watch, with Glass Constellations, Red Vision, and Night Sky Live Tours - all on your wrist! 

- AR OBJECT EXPLORATION  - Pull Planets, Stars and Constellations out of the sky and look at them in detailed AR!

- NIGHT SKY TOURS (+ Feature):  Get a live sky tour or create your own sky tours for any location and time in the world!  

- NIGHT SKY MINDFULNESS (+ Feature) - A mindfulness stargazing experience adding mindfulness minutes with Apple HealthKit. 

- AND MANY MORE FEATURES! 


Subscription Information: 'Night Sky +' and 'Night Sky + Aura' are available as optional subscriptions. Subscriptions renew automatically unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage or cancel anytime in your App Store account settings. Með Já.is appinu finnur þú fólk og fyrirtæki á Íslandi og besta verðið í íslenskum vefverslunum. Í appinu er nafnabirtir sem sýnir upplýsingar um þann sem hringir áður en símtali er svarað. 

Helstu eiginleikar:
 - Símanúmer og heimilisföng einstaklinga og fyrirtækja. 
 - Nafnabirtir, þú sérð hver er að hringja áður en þú svarar. 
 - Vöruleit í öllum íslenskum vefverslunum. 
 - Kort með leiðarvísun og 360° götusýn. 
 - Afgreiðslutímar fyrirtækja 

Þú getur á nokkrum sekúndum fundið það sem þú leitar að, hringt, sent sms skilaboð eða tölvupóst, skoðað staðsetningu á korti, fundið afgreiðslutíma, samfélagsmiðla, umsagnir og stjörnur fyrirtækja. Þú getur skoðað vörur frá öllum íslenskum vefverslunum, gert verðsamanburð og búið til óskalista. Appið byggir á öflugri leitartækni og gögnum frá Já.  
 
Já.is appið er ókeypis. 

----
 
The Ja.is app helps you find people and businesses in Iceland as well as the best product prices in Icelandic web stores. The app also features a caller ID, showing you who’s calling before you answer. 
 
The Ja.is app features include:
 - Telephone numbers and addresses of people and businesses. 
 - Caller display - you see who’s calling before answering. 
 - Product search of all Icelandic web stores simultaneously. 
 - Map with directions and 360° street-view. 
 - Opening hours of businesses. 
  
In just a few seconds, you can find what you‘re looking for, make a phone call, send a text message or an email, view the location on our map, check opening hours, connect via social media, and see star ratings and reviews of businesses. You can view products from every web store in Iceland, compare prices, and make a wish list. The Ja.is app is powered by the extensive database of the Ja.is search engine.  
 
The Ja.is app is free.

FÍTUSAR APPSINS:
 - Veldu hvort þú viljir skoða stelpunöfn eða strákanöfn
 - Merktu við uppáhalds nöfnin þín – stelpu eða strákanöfn
 - Bættu við millinafni og eftirnafni til að sjá hvernig nafnið passar saman
 - Deildu nafnalistanum þínum með maka eða vini
 - Skoðaðu merkingu nafna og hversu margir bera þau á Íslandi
 - Raðaðu uppáhaldsnöfnunum þínum eftir þínum eigin forgangi
 - Leitaðu að nafni eða skoðaðu öll nöfn í stafrófsröð
 - Notaðu ítarlega síu (filter) til að finna hið fullkomna nafn:
        -  Fjöldi stafa
        -  Fjöldi atkvæða
        -  Hvort nafnið byrji eða endi á tilteknum bókstaf
        -  Notkun íslenskra stafa (á, þ, ð, æ o.fl.)

SmáUglan er app, á bæði íslensku og ensku, sem býður upp á persónulega og notendavæna útgáfu af Uglunni, innri vef margra háskóla landsins. Notendur geta lagað SmáUglu-appið að eigin þörfum með því að breyta upphafsskjá og flýtileiðum og þannig valið þá möguleika sem hver og einn notar mest.
 
Í appinu er m.a. hægt að sjá "daginn" þinn sem hefur að geyma yfirlit yfir allar kennslustundir, próf, fundi og viðburði hvern dag, allt á einum stað. Dagurinn breytist svo í vikuryfirlit með því að halla símanum á hlið. Þá geta notendur fylgst með því sem er að gerast í skólanum gegnum fréttir og tilkynningar, séð hvað er í matinn í mötuneytinu og skoðað öll sín námskeið og lokaeinkunnir. Appið bíður einnig upp á að stimpla sig inn og út í gegnum Vinnustund.
 
Notendur skrá sig aðeins einu sinni í appið og eru eftir það ávallt með SmáUgluna tilbúna í vasanum; það eina sem þarf er nettenging! SmáUglan er þægileg viðbót og einföld leið að því sem þú notar oftast í Uglunni.
 
SmáUglan is an app in both Icelandic and English, that offers a personal and user-friendly version of Ugla, the intraweb used by many Icelandic universities. Users can adapt the baby owl, SmáUglan, to their own needs by changing the start-up screen and short-cuts, and choosing the options you use the most.  
 
Among the features of the app is „my day“ which gives you an overview of all your classes, exams, meetings and events each day, all in one place. Your day then changes into your week by tilting the phone on its side. Users can, furthermore, monitor what is happening at their university via news and announcements, see what is for lunch in the cafeteria, and see all their courses and final grades. The app also allows users to clock in and out of Vinnustund.
 
Users only need to sign into the app once the first time it is used, and after that they have the SmáUgla app ready in their pocket; the only thing needed is wi-fi! SmáUglan is a convenient addition and a simple way to access what you use most in Ugla – intraweb.

app_name: Merlin Bird ID by Cornell Lab
description:
What's that bird? Ask Merlin—the world’s leading app for birds. Just like magic, Merlin Bird ID will help you solve the mystery.

Merlin Bird ID helps you identify birds you see and hear. Merlin is unlike any other bird app—it's powered by eBird, the world’s largest database of bird sightings, sounds, and photos.

Merlin offers four fun ways to identify birds. Answer a few simple questions, upload a photo, record a singing bird, or explore birds in a region.

Whether you’re curious about a bird you’ve seen once or you’re hoping to identify every bird you can find, the answers are waiting for you with this free app from the renowned Cornell Lab of Ornithology.

WHY YOU’LL LOVE MERLIN
• Expert ID tips, range maps, photos, and sounds help you learn about the birds you spot and build birding skills.
• Discover a new bird species each day with your own personalized Bird of the Day
• Get customized lists of birds you can find where you live or travel - anywhere in the world!
• Keep track of your sightings—build your personal list of the birds you find

MACHINE LEARNING MAGIC
• Powered by Visipedia, Merlin Sound ID and Photo ID uses machine learning to identify birds in photos and sounds. Merlin learns to recognize bird species based on training sets of millions of photos and sounds collected by birders at eBird.org, archived in the Macaulay Library at the Cornell Lab of Ornithology.
• Merlin delivers the most accurate results thanks to experienced birders, who curate and annotate sightings, photos, and sounds, who are the true magic behind Merlin.

AMAZING CONTENT
• Merlin has bird photos, songs, and calls, and identification help for anywhere in the world, including Mexico, Costa Rica, South America, Europe, Africa, the Middle East, India, Australia, Korea, Japan, China, and more.

The Cornell Lab of Ornithology’s mission is to interpret and conserve the Earth’s biological diversity through research, education, and citizen science focused on birds and nature. We are able to offer Merlin for free thanks to the generosity of Cornell Lab members, supporters, and citizen-science contributors.

Explore your world, find a quick fact, or dive down a Wikipedia rabbit hole with the official Wikipedia app for iOS. With more than 40 million articles across nearly 300 languages, your favorite free online encyclopedia is at your fingertips. 
 
App features: 

Night reading - Appearance controls let you read Wikipedia in comfort, with dark mode, text size control and image dimming to customize how you read. 

Places - Find Wikipedia articles about places next door or across the globe, with a map and location based search experience. On a trip or your daily commute, with Places it’s easy to learn more about the world around you.

Explore feed - Discover the depths of Wikipedia through your explore feed, which surfaces Wikipedia articles and captivating freely-licensed photos. It includes a diverse array of interesting content, including:  
 
- recommended articles based on what you’ve already read
- featured articles hand-picked by the Wikipedia community
- daily top read articles 
- picture of the day
- events on this day in history
- random articles
- nearby landmarks 
 
Find and search -  Easily find what you’re looking for by searching within articles or using Spotlight. You can even search with your favorite emojis! 
 
Quick access - Add Wikipedia to your device's Today screen to pick up exactly where you stopped reading your last article, or see the top-read articles and trends of the day.
 
Easy touch navigation, including 3D touch - Multi-touch gestures like swipe, tap, and 3D Touch features complete essential tasks more quickly and simply. 
 
Save articles - Save articles for reading later, even when you’re offline. Search and sort Saved articles, and organize them into folders. Log in to sync your Reading Lists across the your mobile devices. 
 
Multilingual support - Search for and read Wikipedia articles written in any Wikipedia-supported language — there are nearly 300! 
 
Share - Easily share articles, images, and facts from Wikipedia on social media or by email. Or use Handoff to continue reading articles across your iOS devices.
